title: The One Where Lala & Brock Davies Squash Their Beef
description:
Lala and Brock squash their beef publicly days before Brock & Scheana’s magical wedding in Mexico! They breakdown the explosive #PumpRules reunion from their perspectives, explain how they really worked things out privately not too long after it aired, and admit what they’d each have done differently if given the chance. Lala also offers Brock the opportunity to share his truth in a safe space, and tell the cliff notes’ version of his life story in Australia before moving to the States and meeting Scheana Shay. Plus, they talk parenting styles and struggles, traveling with babies, and good growth moments!
